:13:44.000Z","msg":"其實都係政府做出黎<br />\n年青人用畢身供樓黎維持政府高地價收入<br />\n廢老就享優惠福利<br />\n但又唔諗下佢每份福利下  年青人受左咩痛苦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n回歸二十幾年 看著每年福利傾斜<br />\n公屋戶反而頭等人過很多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有班唔做野呃綜援<br />\n<br />\n出門啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d086d5c3d8d4fbf7610d174c3913815de97a72","tid":1664121,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T02:14:49.000Z","msg":"On9仲信狗"},{"pid":"7513615086076eb44614cef979c690e0018896e2","tid":1664121,"uid":194398,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T02:16:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a854cc6d704c3f1bd6c9c80a142ecf3c2a540d9d","tid":1664121,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"017610e36efa321c501d4aa6a6884d3f343ed387","tid":1664121,"uid":194281,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T01:54:35.000Z","msg":"點解外國咁成功,香港咁失敗<br />\n因為係人既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T02:22:26.000Z","msg":"這就是香港人 全地球最垃圾人種<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643438cb1c14c4e8dc43d9cb245be77fb5ff38d7","tid":1664121,"uid":244262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T02:22:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e31ea9efd9ed8e6d103a597f0f35065b50516f1b","tid":1664121,"uid":73959,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T